data.description:
Charming 2 Bed, 1 Bath Home with RV Parking in Las Vegas!

Welcome to this charming single-story home located in the heart of Las Vegas, you'll enjoy easy access to shopping, dining, parks, and entertainment. 
This well-maintained residence features two spacious bedrooms, a bright and airy living area, and a fully equipped kitchen perfect for all your culinary endeavors.
Key Features:
2 bedrooms * 1 bathroom * Open and inviting floor plan * Kitchen with modern appliances * Convenient * Low-maintenance front and backyard spaces * Plus, the added bonus of RV parking means you have room for all your adventure gear!
This home is a perfect blend of comfort and functionality. The generously sized bedrooms offer plenty of space for relaxation, while the backyard provides a tranquil retreat. With RV parking on site, this property is ideal for outdoor enthusiasts or those seeking extra storage space.
